# Azure Deployment (Full Flow)

## Infrastructure (Terraform)

- **PostgreSQL Flexible Server** — `azurerm_postgresql_flexible_server`; `sslmode=require`; private DNS zone for VNet.
- **Redis Cache** — `rediss://` TLS-only.
- **Container Apps** — API, Worker, Migration Job (one-shot). Sample migration job:

```hcl
resource "azurerm_container_app_job" "migrate" {
  name                         = "caj-${var.project_name}-migrate-${var.environment}"
  container_app_environment_id = azurerm_container_app_environment.main.id
  manual_trigger_config { parallelism = 1; replica_completion_count = 1 }
  template {
    container {
      name    = "migrate"
      image   = var.container_image  # or flyway/flyway
      command = ["flyway", "-url=${var.database_connection_string}", "-locations=filesystem:/flyway/sql", "migrate"]
      env { name = "DATABASE_URL"; value = var.database_connection_string }
    }
  }
}
```

- **Key Vault**: Stores `DATABASE_URL`, `REDIS_URL`, `OPENAI_API_KEY`, Basic Auth, etc.

## Deploy flow (sample)

1. **Build** — Build Docker image, push to ACR.
2. **Migrate** — Start migration Container App Job; wait for completion.
3. **Deploy** — Update API and Worker Container Apps with new image.

```yaml
jobs:
  build-and-push:
    steps: [checkout, docker-login, build-push]
    outputs: { image: ... }
  migrate:
    needs: build-and-push
    steps:
      - run: |
          EXECUTION=$(az containerapp job start --name caj-PROJECT-migrate-ENV --resource-group rg-PROJECT-ENV --query "name" -o tsv)
          for i in $(seq 1 30); do
            STATUS=$(az containerapp job execution show --job-execution-name "$EXECUTION" ... --query "properties.status" -o tsv)
            [ "$STATUS" = "Succeeded" ] && exit 0
            [ "$STATUS" = "Failed" ] && exit 1
            sleep 10
          done
  deploy:
    needs: migrate
    steps:
      - run: az containerapp update --name ca-PROJECT-api-ENV ... --image ${{ needs.build-and-push.outputs.image }}
      - run: az containerapp update --name ca-PROJECT-worker-ENV ... --image ${{ needs.build-and-push.outputs.image }}
```

## Secrets

- `DATABASE_URL`, `REDIS_URL`, `OPENAI_API_KEY` from Key Vault or Container App secrets.
- Migration job receives `DATABASE_URL`; runs Alembic (`alembic upgrade head`) or Flyway (`flyway migrate`).

## Migration job

- One-shot job (manual trigger) before each deploy.
- Command: `flyway migrate` (see sample above) or `python -m alembic upgrade head` if using Alembic.
- See `.cursor/rules/flyway-migrations.mdc` for Flyway details.
